{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji18.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给林伯渠“的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给林伯渠的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年1月19日）林老："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来示诵悉，生产节约今年必比去年有更好成效，你个人的计划能实行，必有好的影响。我也定了一点计划，准备实行。敬祝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健康！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东一月十九日林老："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未不源杰，军约缘七年有知成动，仿个人的漪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，精如的算。我也岔了一生外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代候。苏说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健京!毛泽东致林伯渠信的手稿。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1944,"month":1,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":310,"page_end":311},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}